_sText:
Thank you for downloading gg_metal.

This map is made with unique, high quality textures for a sleek and sharp look, keeping design in the highest of concerns. 

Features a floating disc in which players can launch up to and shoot other unsuspecting players below. There's also plenty of space to take cover.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created by myself.
Skybox texture created by Karatekafer. 

If you'd like to play this map on our gg server, please join us at:

208.146.44.32:27015

or visit us on the fourms:

http://seattle-ducksoup.com/index.php

Thank you!

--Manqueef/Emeriastone
